                        <p>"Once your environment is set up and your guide is written:"</p>
                        
                        <ol>
                            <li>
                                <strong>"Set a Slug:"</strong>" Enter a unique URL identifier for your project in the top navigation bar (e.g., "<code>"my-awesome-cli"</code>")."
